---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { site } from '../data/site';

const updated = '2026-05-24';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Use"
  description={`Terms of use for the ${site.name} website.`}
  ogImage="/branding/og/terms.png"
>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 pt-12 pb-16">
    <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--color-accent-2)]">Legal</p>
    <h1 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl mt-2 tracking-wide">Terms of Use</h1>
    <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-text-dim)] mt-2">Last updated: {updated}</p>

    <div class="prose mt-8 text-[var(--color-text)] leading-relaxed space-y-5">
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mt-2 tracking-wide">Use of the site</h2>
      <p>
        You may access and read this website for personal, non-commercial use.
        You may not scrape, mirror, or republish substantial portions of the site
        without permission. You may link to any page on this site without prior
        notice.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mt-8 tracking-wide">Data attribution</h2>
      <p>
        Roster, match, achievement, and tournament information across this site
        is sourced from
        <a href="https://liquipedia.net/overwatch/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Liquipedia</a>
        and is provided under the
        <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 3.0 license</a>.
        Any reuse of that data must preserve the same license terms and credit
        Liquipedia as the original source.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mt-8 tracking-wide">Game content (Overwatch hero imagery)</h2>
      <p>
        Hero portrait imagery shown on player cards depicts characters from
        <em>Overwatch</em>, which is © Blizzard Entertainment, Inc. The imagery
        is used here as non-commercial fan content under Blizzard's
        <a href="https://www.blizzard.com/en-us/legal/feda9eb3-9d99-4dc8-ab30-3df16626068c/legal-policies-fan-content-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Fan Content Policy</a>.
        Najdorf Esports is not affiliated with, endorsed by, sponsored by, or
        specifically approved by Blizzard Entertainment, and Blizzard is not
        responsible for the content of this site.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mt-8 tracking-wide">Open-source components</h2>
      <p>
        This site is built with the Astro framework (MIT), Tailwind CSS (MIT),
        TypeScript (Apache-2.0), and the Sharp image library (Apache-2.0). Its
        display and body fonts (Anton, Inter) are licensed under the
        <a href="https://scripts.sil.org/OFL" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SIL Open Font License 1.1</a>.
        All open-source notices are preserved in the project's source
        repository.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mt-8 tracking-wide">Trademarks</h2>
      <p>
        <em>Overwatch</em>, the <em>Overwatch Champions Series</em>, and related
        marks are trademarks of Blizzard Entertainment, Inc.
        <em>Twitch</em> is a trademark of Twitch Interactive, Inc., an Amazon
        subsidiary. <em>X</em> (formerly Twitter) is a trademark of X Corp.
        All other trademarks shown on this site belong to their respective
        owners. Use of these marks here is purely descriptive and does not
        imply affiliation, endorsement, or sponsorship.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mt-8 tracking-wide">No commercial transactions yet</h2>
      <p>
        This website does not currently sell goods or services. The "Shop"
        placeholder page is provided as a notice of future availability only.
        When the store launches, separate terms of sale will apply.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mt-8 tracking-wide">No warranty</h2>
      <p>
        This site is provided on an "as is" basis without warranties of any kind.
        Match schedules, results, and roster information are subject to change.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mt-8 tracking-wide">Copyright complaints (DMCA / equivalent)</h2>
      <p>
        If you believe content on this site infringes a copyright you own or
        control, email {site.contactEmail} with: (1) identification of the
        copyrighted work, (2) the URL of the allegedly infringing material,
        (3) your contact information, and (4) a good-faith statement that the
        use is not authorized. We will respond promptly and remove material
        that we agree is infringing.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mt-8 tracking-wide">Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about these terms: {site.contactEmail}.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style is:global>
  .prose p { margin-bottom: 1em; }
  .prose a { color: var(--color-accent-2); text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 3px; }
  .prose a:hover { color: var(--color-accent); }
</style>
